<div class="Anchortitle">
<h1 id="top">Reference Service</h1>

<h3><strong><a href="#Research"><span style="color:#0000cc;">1.Research consultation</span></a></strong></h3>

<h3><strong><a href="#E-Resource"><span style="color:#0000cc;">2.E-Resource Service</span></a></strong></h3>
</div>

<div class="context">
<h4 id="Research"><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">1.Research consultation</span></h4>

<h4><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">The Library offers a one-on-one research consultation service to all NTUST faculty members and students to assist them in</span></h4>

<h4><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">-Identifying information needs</span></h4>

<h4><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">-Locating resources most relevant to their research projects</span></h4>

<h4><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">-Constructing effective search techniques</span></h4>

<h4><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">-Searching electronic and print resources effectively</span></h4>

<h4><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">-Evaluating the resources used</span></h4>

<h4><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">Other Research Assistance</span></h4>

<h4><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">You can contact the reference librarian directly for research assistance or by email, phonecall..etc.</span></h4>

<h4><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">General and specific workshops and seminars are arranged from time to time. Please check our programs and register.</span></h4>

<div>&nbsp;</div>

<div id="E-Resource"><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">2.E-Resource Service</span></div>

<h4><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">The library has subscribed to a wide variety of online resources including e-books,</span></h4>

<h4><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">periodicals and newspapers, thesis and dissertations, conference proceedings,</span></h4>

<h4><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">encyclopedias, and multimedia databases.</span></h4>

<h4><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">Discovery System is a one-stop search system for large amounts of print and online content, including most of NTUST&rsquo;S collections.</span></h4>

<h4><span style="font-family:微軟正黑體;">Users could easily access to our e-resources in campus or outside the campus.</span></h4>

